    ACL='public-read',
    Bucket='test-bucket-xxx',
)
使用自定义的ACL可指定的Permission包括：'FULL_CONTROL', 'WRITE', 'WRITE_ACP', 'READ', 'READ_ACP'resp = cli.put_bucket_acl(
    AccessControlPolicy={
        'Grants': [
            {
                'Grantee': {
                    'ID': 'user_foo', # 请替换为真实存在的用户
                    'Type': 'CanonicalUser',
                },
